channel.title: Was this part of a beat the clock?
channel.description:
I found this video on my SSD while looking for places to free up storage space, but I don't remember making it. Judging by the image used (the very first version of my logo) it's likely from sometime in early-mid 2017 or 2016. It sounds like something I could have come up with on my own back then, but I can't tell for sure. That said, it leads me to wonder if it could have been part of an early beat the clock.
https://youtu.be/D2Kr289KrVE
